        <span class="l-zh">托福备考日记</span><span class="l-tw">托福備考日記</span><span class="l-en">TOEFL Prep Diary</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="tab-panel" id="tab-toefl" role="tabpanel">
      <div class="empty">
        <div class="icon">✎</div>
        <h4><span class="l-zh">备考日记整理中</span><span class="l-tw">備考日記整理中</span><span class="l-en">Diary coming together</span></h4>
        <p>
          <span class="l-zh">给我几条日记就行：日期 + 当天做了什么（背单词、刷 TPO、口语练习…）+ 分数或感受。我会排成上面这样的时间线，目标分数也可以单独标出来。</span>
          <span class="l-tw">給我幾條日記就行：日期 + 當天做了什麼（背單字、刷 TPO、口語練習…）+ 分數或感受。我會排成上面這樣的時間線，目標分數也可以單獨標出來。</span>
          <span class="l-en">Just send me a few entries: date + what you did that day (vocab, TPO sets, speaking practice…) + a score or how it felt. I'll lay them out as a timeline, and we can call out a target score too.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tab-panel show" id="tab-code" role="tabpanel">
      <div class="reads-lab"><span class="l-zh">在跟的学习仓库</span><span class="l-tw">在跟的學習倉庫</span><span class="l-en">Repo I'm following</span></div>
      <div class="reads">
        <a class="read" href="https://github.com/datawhalechina/every-embodied" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <div class="rtags"><span class="rtag"><span class="l-zh">具身智能</span><span class="l-tw">具身智能</span><span class="l-en">Embodied AI</span></span><span class="rtag">Open source</span><span class="rtag">2.2k★</span></div>
          <h4>Every-Embodied · Zero to Hero in Embodied AI</h4>
          <div class="src">datawhalechina</div>
          <p>
            <span class="l-zh">仅需 Python 基础，从 0 构建自己的具身智能机器人，逐步实现 VLA / OpenVLA / SmolVLA / Pi0。三阶段路线：机器人学与 ROS 基础 → CV / 运动规划 / 强化学习 → 模仿学习与大模型（VLA/VLN）、Sim2Real。我正跟着它系统学习具身智能。</span>
            <span class="l-tw">僅需 Python 基礎，從 0 構建自己的具身智能機器人，逐步實現 VLA / OpenVLA / SmolVLA / Pi0。三階段路線：機器人學與 ROS 基礎 → CV / 運動規劃 / 強化學習 → 模仿學習與大模型（VLA/VLN）、Sim2Real。我正跟著它系統學習具身智能。</span>
            <span class="l-en">Build your own embodied-AI robot from zero with only Python basics, working up to VLA / OpenVLA / SmolVLA / Pi0. Three stages: robotics + ROS basics → CV / motion planning / RL → imitation learning, VLA/VLN, and Sim2Real. The path I'm following to learn embodied AI.</span>
          </p>
          <span class="go"><span class="l-zh">查看仓库</span><span class="l-tw">查看倉庫</span><span class="l-en">View repo</span> <span class="arrow">→</span></span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="books-note">
        <span class="l-zh">下一轮把你自己的学习里程碑发我（学过 / 在学的语言与方向：Python、爬虫、ROS、前端、AI…），我会排成一条带「已完成 / 进行中」标记的路径。</span>
        <span class="l-tw">下一輪把你自己的學習里程碑發我（學過 / 在學的語言與方向：Python、爬蟲、ROS、前端、AI…），我會排成一條帶「已完成 / 進行中」標記的路徑。</span>
        <span class="l-en">Next round, send me your own milestones (languages/areas you've learned or are learning: Python, crawlers, ROS, frontend, AI…) and I'll lay them out as a path marked done vs. in progress.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
